{"tid":1646354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［幫手repost］中聯辦喺香港嘅物業","createTime":"2019-10-11T09:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:20:33.000Z","uid":183122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"26a3597e880c1ee163651ed5be6e7e67120e4c43","tid":1646354,"uid":183122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三大中共入侵香港的辦公室</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中聯辦</span></span><br />\n香港物業非常多！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDbQnjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDbQnjp.png&h=085fbb90&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n特別可以留意三大辦公室位置 <br />\n佢仲要用依啲物業黎炒樓，仲要可以免稅！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新華社</span></strong></span><br />\n一直大家都冇留意到佢，係中共既情報機構同埋宣傳、統戰部門<br />\n地址： 皇后大道東381號 （灣仔）<br />\n就係伊館對面！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中共外交駐港特派專員公署</span></strong><br />\n一樣係統戰部門！<br />\n半山堅尼地道42號  （金鐘上半山）<br />\n<br />\n就睇下，警方你要用幾多兵先守得到咁多個地方！<br />\n大家快閃又可以諗多幾個地方，睇下你死守到幾多個地方！"}]}